        "source": "# Check that Italy wins more home games than it loses home games.\nitaly_stats = country_stats[country_stats['country'] == 'Italy']\nassert not italy_stats.empty, \"Italy not found in the stats DataFrame.\"\nhome_wins = italy_stats['wins_home'].iloc[0]\nhome_losses = italy_stats['losses_home'].iloc[0]\nassert home_wins > home_losses, \"Assertion failed: Italy should have more home wins than home losses.\""
       }
