        "source": "import pandas as pd\n\n# Create a small sample dataset of soccer match results\ndata = {\n    'date': ['2023-01-01', '2023-01-05', '2023-01-10', '2023-01-15', '2023-01-20'],\n    'home_team': ['Brazil', 'Argentina', 'Germany', 'Brazil', 'Argentina'],\n    'away_team': ['Argentina', 'Germany', 'Brazil', 'Germany', 'Brazil'],\n    'home_score': [3, 1, 0, 2, 0],\n    'away_score': [1, 1, 2, 2, 1],\n    'tournament': ['Friendly'] * 5,\n    'city': ['Rio', 'Buenos Aires', 'Berlin', 'Rio', 'Buenos Aires'],\n    'country': ['Brazil', 'Argentina', 'Germany', 'Brazil', 'Argentina'],\n    'neutral': [False] * 5\n}\n\ndf = pd.DataFrame(data)\n\nprint(\"Sample dataset (df):\")\nprint(df.to_string(index=False))"
       },
